testsuite.name: datadog.communication.http.HttpRetryPolicyTest

testcase.name: test exponential backoff is applied to retries [maxRetries: 0, delayMs: 100, delayMultiplier: 2.0, expectedShouldRetries: [false], expectedBackoffs: [], #0]
test exponential backoff is applied to retries [maxRetries: 1, delayMs: 100, delayMultiplier: 2.0, expectedShouldRetries: [true, false], expectedBackoffs: [100], #1]
test exponential backoff is applied to retries [maxRetries: 2, delayMs: 100, delayMultiplier: 2.0, expectedShouldRetries: [true, true, false], expectedBackoffs: [100, 200], #2]
test exponential backoff is applied to retries [maxRetries: 3, delayMs: 100, delayMultiplier: 2.0, expectedShouldRetries: [true, true, true, false], expectedBackoffs: [100, 200, 400], #3]
test exponential backoff is applied to retries [maxRetries: 4, delayMs: 100, delayMultiplier: 2.0, expectedShouldRetries: [true, true, true, true, false], expectedBackoffs: [100, 200, 400, 800], #4]

test exponential backoff is applied to retries [maxRetries: 5, delayMs: 100, delayMultiplier: 2.0, expectedShouldRetries: [true, true, true, true, true, false], expectedBackoffs: [100, 200, 400, 800, 1600], #5]
test there are 0 retries for response code 200 and rate limit header null
test there are 0 retries for response code 404 and rate limit header null
test there are 5 retries for response code 429 and rate limit header null
test there are 5 retries for response code 429 and rate limit header corrupted
test there are 1 retries for response code 429 and rate limit header 2
test there are 0 retries for response code 429 and rate limit header 20
test there are 5 retries for response code 500 and rate limit header null
test there are 5 retries for response code 501 and rate limit header null
test exceptions are retried: java.lang.NullPointerException with suppress interrupts false
test exceptions are retried: java.lang.IllegalArgumentException with suppress interrupts false
test exceptions are retried: java.net.ConnectException with suppress interrupts false
test exceptions are retried: java.io.InterruptedIOException with suppress interrupts false
test exceptions are retried: java.io.InterruptedIOException with suppress interrupts true
test exceptions are retried: java.lang.InterruptedException with suppress interrupts false
test exceptions are retried: java.lang.InterruptedException with suppress interrupts true
test interrupt flag is preserved when suppressing interrupts
test interrupt flag is preserved if interrupted while backing off
